00:01:24.590 --> 00:01:26.050
Let's break it down.

00:01:26.050 --> 00:01:30.130
Dr. Shakashiri started with
two clear, colorless liquids.

00:01:30.130 --> 00:01:36.560
He had about 100
milliliters of lead nitrate.

00:01:39.309 --> 00:01:40.100
